description: PW 04 was born on 20 June 2021 at VulPro. PW 04 was born in nest 2 in the open enclosure to his parents Steve and TB 33, and was incubated and raised by them. Steve was originally paired up with Ruth, but unfortunately died at the beginning of the year. This is the first season he has paired up with TB 33 and they are both first time parents as Steve and Ruth, despite being partnered up, never laid a successful egg.
name: Purple White 04
